  "instructions": [
    "Preheat grill to medium-high heat.",
    "In a large bowl, whisk together tagine spice blend, 2 tablespoons olive oil, and 1 tablespoon lemon juice.",
    "Add the chicken to the bowl and toss to coat with the spice mixture.",
    "Grill the chicken for 5-7 minutes per side, or until cooked through.",
    "Meanwhile, toast the flatbread on the grill or in a toaster.",
